items.name: Easy-HangMan-Games
items.description: This Python script implements a fun Hangman game. It randomly selects a word from categories like animals, food, cities, countries, places, and birds. Players guess one letter at a time, with six lives. Incorrect guesses are visualized with a hangman figure. The game ends when lives run out or the word is guessed.
